      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，阿克曼计划最早于 2025 年让潘兴广场进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ackman-plans-pershing-square-ipo-as-soon-as-2025-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，对冲基金经理比尔·阿克曼计划最早于明年让其投资公司潘兴广场 (Pershing Square) 首次公开募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ackman-plans-pershing-square-ipo-as-soon-as-2025-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:27:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
